+- Downstream impacted surfaces: `OperationalApp`, role-specific page gating, session preferences, remote repositories, academic bootstrap payload
+- Trigger: app load, login submit, session restore, role switch, preference save
+- Data contract or key fields: `ApiSessionResponse`, `availableRoleGrants`, `activeRoleGrant.roleCode`, `preferences.themeMode`
